# Strategy for PRS
1. Hail script to export file of sparse gentotypes for calculating kinship
2. bash script to run LDAK to calcualte kinship
3. Hail script that can write out pre-imputed genotypes as .bed/.bgen files
4. Single predictor analysis using genotypes (3) kinship matrix (2) and phenotypes in plink format
